Lint:
- npm run lint

Cleanup:
- npm prune --production=false
- npm dedupe
- node -e "require('fs').rmSync('.next',{recursive:true,force:true});require('fs').rmSync('coverage',{recursive:true,force:true})"

Build (production):
- npm run clean-build

Run tests:
- npm test

Start (development):
- npm run dev

Start (production preview):
- npm run clean-build
- npm run start

Git (stage, commit, push):
- git add .
- git commit -m "Welcome flow polish: card width + image column; curved-square logo; hydration-safe labels; tests green"
- git push

Notes:
- Hydration fix: compute welcome labels in useEffect and render label text only when ready.
- Analytics: disabled during SSR/tests to avoid invalid URL errors.
